query:
UPDATE calendar_events SET
                external_parent_id = $2,
                external_id = $3,
                title = $4,
                description = $5,
                event_type = $6,
                location = $7,
                status = $8,
                all_day = $9,
                start_time = $10,
                duration = $11,
                end_time = $12,
                busy = $13,
                created = $14,
                updated = $15,
                recurrence = $16,
                recurring_until = $17,
                exdates = $18,
                recurring_event_uid = $19,
                original_start_time = $20,
                reminders = $21,
                service_uid = $22,
                metadata = $23
            WHERE event_uid = $1
